  "description": "A simple microphone daemon and websocket wrapper for streaming audio chunks to and from the Car Thing. Some ADB configuration is required as well as access to SupervisorCTL.",
  "keywords": [
    "DeskThing",
    "Microphone",
    "Car",
    "Thing",
    "Car",
